				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="9e04bbe0-0785-46e6-ae30-b5dc374d6667">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/graduate/indigenous-graduate-education/amanda-720.jpg" alt="Indigenous students speaking at a podium"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>There are a number of scholarships, awards and opportunities available to Indigenous graduate students. If you have questions about these scholarships or opportunities, please contact the program directly.</p>
</div>
						    
					
