                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1508788996446-ryerson-faculty-association-award----2-500" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#7be531a2-71b1-47c4-bffb-6070de5cb2ab" href="#accordion-content-1508788996446-ryerson-faculty-association-award----2-500" aria-controls="accordion-content-1508788996446-ryerson-faculty-association-award----2-500" aria-expanded="false">
                            Ryerson Faculty Association Award - $2,500
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1508788996446-ryerson-faculty-association-award----2-500" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1508788996446-ryerson-faculty-association-award----2-500">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1508788996446 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="3c1dbe2b-af50-4498-84da-fcc4261a0cc5" >

    <p>To be eligible students must be of Aboriginal Ancestry (First Nations, Inuit, Metis, non-Status, Status), must have a good academic record, must be studying at Ryerson full or part-time, and must write an essay. Awards will be awarded to one undergraduate student and one graduate student.</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Applicant must have clear academic standing.</li> 
 <li>Applicant must be of Aboriginal Ancestry.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>Apply in <a href="https://ryerson.awardspring.ca/Dashboard">Award Spring<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a>.</p>
    





